 Erie Shores 3-Ironman 
Erie Shores Golf Course 
Sat Oct 29, 2011 | 09:00 AM 
Scramble Format, Professional, Amateur, 3-Player Team Event 
      
    Your Street Address         
 Ê 
 TOURNAMENT DETAILS: Ironman 3-Man Cash Scramble at Erie Shores Golf Club. 
 Extreme tee and pin positions. Teams of one professional/ two ams or 3-amateurs. 
 Cost Per Event 
$135/team includes golf/cart & team entry. 
$60/team Ð Skins Game (optional) 
$30/team Ð Extra Pot (optional) 
$15/team Ð Pinshots (optional) 
 Tee times from 9am Ð 11am. Call (440) 428-3164 to sign-up or  email Brian Perkins . 
 
